#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
New Threat

  Since the Equinox attack, the new Unknown fighters have attacked GTA ships and stations on 47 separate occasions.  All GTA ships have been ordered to scan any hostiles if the possibility arises, and to obtain information on them at all costs.
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
Presidential Inauguration

  On a brighter note, the inauguration of Commodore Robert April as the new GTA president occured this morning.  Commodore April has served the GTA for over 25 years, and was present at First Contact with the Vasudans.  He also played an instrumental part in the Terran-Vasudan war, as well as coordinating some fleet movements and tactical plans during the Shivan War.
  In his inaugural speech today, Commodore April discussed such current issues as the Unknowns, the VERC (Vasudan Economical Restoration Committee), and the current GTA budget.
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

