   The Bozeman safely made it to Aldeberan, and the Equinox survivors have confirmed our worst fears.  It seems that the Shivans were in fact not destroyed seven years ago, as we until recently thought.  Our findings have been forwarded to GTA Command, and a copy of this information is reaching the President's desk as we speak. Excellent work today, pilot.  You are to be commended.
$end_multi_text
